keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
map g focusInput
map e scrollPageUp
map q previousTab
map w nextTab
map a goBack
map s goForward
map E scrollToTop
map D scrollToBottom
map z Vomnibar.activateInNewTab
unmap t
map t duplicateTab
map T createTab
